      "description": "Check out this dependable daily driver! This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go with ease. It shows some honest character with expected cosmetic wear and minor signs of use, but it remains a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for functional transportation at a great price. Perfect for a first car or a commute-ready workhorse!",
