    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior presents well, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches from regular use. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only minimal wear on the upholstery and steering wheel. All major systems are functioning properly, and it provides a smooth, confident driving experience.",
