    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The power delivery is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanical highlights include a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent Double VANOS overhaul, ensuring the variable valve timing operates at peak efficiency. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative steering feel this chassis is famous for. A well-maintained enthusiast machine optimized for lateral Gs and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
