    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury SUV, offering a seamless blend of comfort and longevity. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical marks of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are free of cracks or stains, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof and navigation suite, operate perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio from the local dealership. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, a new cabin air filter, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a trip to the shop anytime soon. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that drives as smoothly as it looks.",
